<h1>Providing the professional touch to campus events</h1>
<p>Operating from the Production Suite in the BYU-Idaho Center, A/V Productions provides professional, high-tech production services. Complemented by a team of skilled students, our team of full-time A/V department professional provide audio/visual productions from the diverse venues located across the the BYU-Idaho campus.</p>
<p>Our services include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Audio and visual support for campus productions</li>
<li>Weekly devotionals and broadcasts</li>
<li>Audio/visual production equipment maintenance</li>
<li>Media transfer</li>
<li>Video production</li>
<li>Webcasting and streaming </li>
</ul>
<p>Requests for support from A/V Productions are initiated through the Scheduling Office (208) 496-3122. Requests are directly associated with the space reserved, and limited to events calendared at BYU-Idaho.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="Component" Component="x42539" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_BannerAd" Name="BannerAds" label="Rotating Ads" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="BannerAd" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="QuickLinks" label="Quick Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="Quick Links Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="Quick Links Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="Quick Links Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Insert" Insert="" WellFormed="false" ExtractHTMLBody="false" Name="HTMLInsert" label="Insert" readonly="false" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x40199" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="false" required="fa